<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV34">
<l>citaikkiṉṟa tāḻiyeṉ ṟāḻiyaic cīṟittaṉ cīṟaṭiyā</l>
<l>lutaikkiṉṟa nāyakan taṉṉoṭu mālē yuṉatutaṇṭār</l>
<l>tataikkiṉṟa taṇṇan tuḻāyaṇi vāṉatu vēmaṉamāyp</l>
<l>pataikkiṉṟa mātiṉ tiṟattaṟi yēñceyaṟ pālatuvē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>We don’t know what is to be done on behalf of the woman who quivers,</l>
<l>[her] mind being on that only: to adorn [herself] with the dense, cool Tulsi</l>
<l>from your cool chaplet, Māl, with the imperiousness in which she kicks</l>
<l>with [her] small foot, raging against the sea, saying it spoils [her] circle.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
